{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.1","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:1","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus en P\u00e9r\u00e9e. Le divorce et le c\u00e9libat<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. Mc 10:1-12. (De 24:1-4. Mt 5:31, 32. 1 Co 7.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Lorsque J\u00e9sus eut achev\u00e9 ces discours, il quitta la Galil\u00e9e, et alla dans le territoire de la Jud\u00e9e, au-del\u00e0 du Jourdain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.2","name":"Matthieu 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.35","name":"Matthieu 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.2","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:2","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Une grande foule le suivit, et l\u00e0 il gu\u00e9rit les malades.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.3","name":"Matthieu 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.1","name":"Matthieu 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.3","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:3","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Les pharisiens l\u2019abord\u00e8rent, et dirent, pour l\u2019\u00e9prouver: Est-il permis \u00e0 un homme de r\u00e9pudier sa femme pour un motif quelconque?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.4","name":"Matthieu 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.2","name":"Matthieu 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.4","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:4","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">N\u2019avez-vous pas lu que le cr\u00e9ateur,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">au commencement, fit l\u2019homme et la femme<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.5","name":"Matthieu 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.3","name":"Matthieu 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.5","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:5","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et qu\u2019il dit: C\u2019est pourquoi l\u2019homme quittera son p\u00e8re et sa m\u00e8re, et s\u2019attachera \u00e0 sa femme, et<\/span><span class=\"wj\">les deux deviendront une seule chair?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.6","name":"Matthieu 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.4","name":"Matthieu 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.6","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:6","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ainsi ils ne sont plus deux, mais ils sont une seule chair.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Que l\u2019homme donc ne s\u00e9pare pas ce que Dieu a joint.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.7","name":"Matthieu 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.5","name":"Matthieu 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.7","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:7","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Pourquoi donc, lui dirent-ils, Mo\u00efse a-t-il prescrit de donner \u00e0 la femme une lettre de divorce et de la r\u00e9pudier?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.8","name":"Matthieu 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.6","name":"Matthieu 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.8","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:8","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est \u00e0 cause de la duret\u00e9 de votre c\u0153ur que Mo\u00efse vous a permis de r\u00e9pudier vos femmes; au commencement, il n\u2019en \u00e9tait pas ainsi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.9","name":"Matthieu 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.7","name":"Matthieu 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.9","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:9","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais je vous dis que celui qui r\u00e9pudie sa femme, sauf pour infid\u00e9lit\u00e9, et qui en \u00e9pouse une autre, commet un adult\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.10","name":"Matthieu 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.8","name":"Matthieu 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.10","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:10","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ses disciples lui dirent: Si telle est la condition de l\u2019homme \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de la femme, il n\u2019est pas avantageux de se marier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.11","name":"Matthieu 19:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.9","name":"Matthieu 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.11","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:11","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Tous ne comprennent pas cette parole, mais seulement ceux \u00e0 qui cela est donn\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.12","name":"Matthieu 19:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.10","name":"Matthieu 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.12","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:12","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car il y a des eunuques qui le sont d\u00e8s le ventre de leur m\u00e8re; il y en a qui le sont devenus par les hommes; et il y en a qui se sont rendus tels eux-m\u00eames, \u00e0 cause du royaume des cieux. Que celui qui peut comprendre comprenne.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.13","name":"Matthieu 19:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.11","name":"Matthieu 19:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.13","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:13","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les petits enfants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-15: cf. (Mc 10:13-16. Lu 18:15-17.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\n    Alors on lui amena des petits enfants, afin qu\u2019il leur impos\u00e2t les mains et pri\u00e2t pour eux. Mais les disciples les repouss\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.14","name":"Matthieu 19:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.12","name":"Matthieu 19:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.14","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:14","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et J\u00e9sus dit: <span class=\"wj\">Laissez les petits enfants, et ne les emp\u00eachez pas de venir \u00e0 moi; car le royaume des cieux est pour ceux qui leur ressemblent.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.15","name":"Matthieu 19:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.13","name":"Matthieu 19:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.15","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:15","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il leur imposa les mains, et il partit de l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.16","name":"Matthieu 19:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.14","name":"Matthieu 19:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.16","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:16","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le jeune homme riche<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-26: cf. (Mc 10:17-27. Lu 18:18-27.) 1 Ti 6:9, 10, 17-19.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Et voici, un homme s\u2019approcha, et dit \u00e0 J\u00e9sus: Ma\u00eetre, que dois-je faire de bon pour avoir la vie \u00e9ternelle?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.17","name":"Matthieu 19:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.15","name":"Matthieu 19:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.17","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:17","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il lui r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Pourquoi m\u2019interroges-tu sur ce qui est bon? Un seul est le bon. Si tu veux entrer dans la vie, observe les commandements.<\/span> Lesquels? Lui dit-il.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.18","name":"Matthieu 19:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.16","name":"Matthieu 19:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.18","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:18","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et J\u00e9sus r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Tu ne tueras point; tu ne commettras point d\u2019adult\u00e8re; tu ne d\u00e9roberas point; tu ne diras point de faux t\u00e9moignage;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.19","name":"Matthieu 19:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.17","name":"Matthieu 19:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.19","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:19","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">honore ton p\u00e8re et ta m\u00e8re; et:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">tu aimeras ton prochain comme toi-m\u00eame.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.20","name":"Matthieu 19:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.18","name":"Matthieu 19:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.20","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:20","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Le jeune homme lui dit: J\u2019ai observ\u00e9 toutes ces choses; que me manque-t-il encore?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.21","name":"Matthieu 19:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.19","name":"Matthieu 19:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.21","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:21","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>J\u00e9sus lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Si tu veux \u00eatre parfait,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">va, vends ce que tu poss\u00e8des,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">donne-le aux pauvres, et tu auras un tr\u00e9sor dans le ciel. Puis viens, et suis-moi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.22","name":"Matthieu 19:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.20","name":"Matthieu 19:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.22","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:22","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir entendu ces paroles, le jeune homme s\u2019en alla tout triste; car il avait de grands biens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.23","name":"Matthieu 19:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.21","name":"Matthieu 19:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.23","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:23","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>J\u00e9sus dit \u00e0 ses disciples: <span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">un riche entrera difficilement dans le royaume des cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.24","name":"Matthieu 19:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.22","name":"Matthieu 19:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.24","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:24","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis encore, il est plus facile \u00e0 un chameau de passer par le trou d\u2019une aiguille qu\u2019\u00e0 un riche d\u2019entrer dans le royaume de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.25","name":"Matthieu 19:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.23","name":"Matthieu 19:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.25","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:25","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Les disciples, ayant entendu cela, furent tr\u00e8s \u00e9tonn\u00e9s, et dirent: Qui peut donc \u00eatre sauv\u00e9?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.26","name":"Matthieu 19:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.24","name":"Matthieu 19:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.26","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:26","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>J\u00e9sus les regarda, et leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Aux hommes cela est impossible,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">mais \u00e0 Dieu tout est possible.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.27","name":"Matthieu 19:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.25","name":"Matthieu 19:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.27","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:27","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.028,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019h\u00e9ritage de la vie \u00e9ternelle<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 27-30: cf. (Mc 10:28-31. Lu 18:28-30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>\n    Pierre, prenant alors la parole, lui dit: Voici, nous avons tout quitt\u00e9, et nous t\u2019avons suivi; qu\u2019en sera-t-il pour nous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.28","name":"Matthieu 19:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.26","name":"Matthieu 19:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.28","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:28","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>J\u00e9sus leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, quand le Fils de l\u2019homme, au renouvellement de toutes choses, sera assis sur le tr\u00f4ne de sa gloire, vous qui m\u2019avez suivi,<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">vous serez de m\u00eame assis sur douze tr\u00f4nes, et vous jugerez les douze tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.29","name":"Matthieu 19:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.27","name":"Matthieu 19:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.29","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:29","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quiconque aura quitt\u00e9, \u00e0 cause de mon nom, ses fr\u00e8res, ou ses s\u0153urs, ou son p\u00e8re, ou sa m\u00e8re, ou sa femme, ou ses enfants, ou ses terres, ou ses maisons,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">recevra le centuple, et h\u00e9ritera la vie \u00e9ternelle.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.30","name":"Matthieu 19:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.28","name":"Matthieu 19:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.30","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 19:30","prev_osis_id":"Matt.019.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.020.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.19.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Plusieurs des premiers seront les derniers, et plusieurs des derniers seront les premiers.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.19","name":"Matthieu 19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.20.1","name":"Matthieu 20:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.20.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.29","name":"Matthieu 19:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb7d3fc45.25327760');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7d3fc45.25327760\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb7d3fc45.25327760","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb7d3fc45.25327760'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7d3fc45.25327760\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}